Changed sample_id from APCL14_131 to NULL. This sample failed to sequence.  When I went to add a note about failed sequencing to the Leyte database, APCL14_131 is not in the Leyte database because the sample # 131 collected in 2014 was an anemone, not a clownfish.  Ligation L2245 blasts to a damsel fish.  It is also hard to believe that while I was separating out vials of clownfish and anemones and labeling them as such, I would mistake an anemone sample for a clownfish sample.  I think that a clownfish sample was collected but not recorded on the data sheet.
